                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.6363/775: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hayes</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-04-17T11:00:00-04:00"
                            >April 17, 1943—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>882. Your 897, April 13, midnight. As this matter is still being discussed here
                    the Department feels it would be premature to make any communication to the
                    Spanish Government at present.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
